ZH: 我的家族来自中国。
EN: My family comes from China.

ZH: 这个部落是他的祖先的族居。
EN: This tribe is where his ancestors lived.

ZH: 他们是一个非常团结的族群。
EN: They are a very close-knit ethnic group.

ZH: 在这个族群中，人们都彼此帮助。
EN: In this ethnic group, people help each other.

ZH: 非洲部落是一个非常独特的族群。
EN: African tribes are a very unique ethnic group.

ZH: 美国有很多不同种族和族群。
EN: America has many different races and ethnic groups.

ZH: 他们的婚姻使两个族群联合了起来。
EN: Their marriage united two ethnic groups.

ZH: 他对祖先的族谱做了详细的研究。
EN: He did a detailed research on his ancestors' genealogy.

ZH: 这个部落有着自己独特的文化和族俗。
EN: This tribe has its own unique culture and customs.

ZH: 随着时间的推移，族群的习俗也发生了变化。
EN: With the passage of time, the customs of the ethnic group have changed.

ZH: 他们的祖先是高山上的原始部落。
EN: Their ancestors were a primitive tribe in the mountains.

ZH: 这个团体是一个由强大族群组成的联盟。
EN: This organization is an alliance made up of powerful ethnic groups.

ZH: 在这个族群中，人们相互尊重。
EN: In this ethnic group, people respect each other.

ZH: 这个村庄里生活着很多不同族群的人。
EN: There are people from many different ethnic groups living in this village.

ZH: 他们的传统艺术是族群文化的重要组成部分。
EN: Their traditional art is an important part of ethnic group culture.

ZH: 进入这个神秘的族群会受到神圣的礼遇。
EN: Entering this mysterious ethnic group will be treated with sacred rituals.

ZH: 族群间的冲突导致了很多血腥战争。
EN: Conflicts between ethnic groups have led to many bloody wars.

ZH: 这个社区里居住着多个不同族群的人。
EN: There are people from multiple different ethnic groups living in this community.

ZH: 在这个国家，族群的多样性是一种财富。
EN: In this country, the diversity of ethnic groups is a wealth.

ZH: 他热爱研究各个族群的历史和传统。
EN: He loves to study the history and traditions of various ethnic groups.
